parameters.name: sql
parameters.value: 'Select cpt.pizza_id, cpt.pizza_name, cpt2.pizza_type_name, cps.pizza_size_name from bl_3nf.ce_pizzas cpt LEFT JOIN bl_3nf.ce_pizzas_types cpt2 ON cpt.pizza_type_id = cpt2.pizza_type_id LEFT JOIN bl_3nf.ce_pizzas_sizes cps ON cpt.pizza_size_id = cps.pizza_size_id WHERE pizza_id > 0 ORDER BY cpt.pizza_name, cpt2.pizza_type_name, cps.pizza_size_name;'
